Lejdud-agi irkulli tijmaɛin n tmes icerreg ; mkul tikkelt ur nezmir ara a d-nețțak seg ulamma d yiwet n tikkelt ; wid yețxebbiṛen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, yețṛaǧu deg-sen a ten-rebḥen. Wid akk yumnen s Lmasiḥ wayes ara bḍuṛen iman-nsen di leqdic ɣef Sidi Ṛebbi nețța akk-d wukrif-nni.
lameɛna amdebbeṛ di tejmaɛt n temdint n Lquds, yețțusemman Yuḥenna, yekker-ed tabṛaț-nni i wid ur numin ara s Ɛisa Lmasiḥ iwakken a t-id-isbeggen s tikli-ines akk-d yemdanen ur nesɛi lmeɛna.
Ay arrac imeẓyanen, inehhu-ten s țțawint lemwaji, luluf-nwen ț-țuṛefti, akk-d leɣla nsen i webrid, ayagi d ayen i gɛeǧben i Sidi Ṛebbi.
Yerna m'ur sɛint ara ayen ara xedment, ad țcalint seg wexxam ɣer wayeḍ mačči imi ur sɛin ara ccɣel, meɛna ad kettṛent deg yimeslayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna, ad ggarent iman-nsent deg wayen i tent-yexḍan.
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : Atah wayen yuklalen ad ițwaḥseb d amecṭuḥ. Di tmurt-nni, axaṭer yețnerni seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit, yerna ț-țura aț-țesbeddeḍ di taɛeryan.
Imezdaɣ n temdint n Atinya akk-d ibeṛṛaniyen i gzedɣen dinna, ḥemmlen ad sɛeddin lweqt-nsen anagar deg umeslay d usmeḥses i lexbaṛat ijdiden i d-ițeffɣen.
Yerna m'ara d-inefk lemtel-agi : ayen yesɛan azal d lɛaddat-nneɣ, ad nemmeslay ɣef temsalin ilsawen-nsen ssefhem, ad nehhun s ṭṭmana mbla ma d ayen sɛan imawen, am wid n diri akk-d licaṛat.
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : « ț-țaseɛdit s tessufuɣen seg wul,» anagar ayen i sen-yexdem ; inelmaden-is ur neṣfi ara, qebblen-d m'ara d-yaweḍ wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Feṛqet di lɛaddat-nsen.
Ini daɣen i temɣarin ad sɛunt tikli yeṣfan, ur ilaq ara ad ilint ț-țiqeṛṛaḍin, ur ilaq ara ad țḥawalent tissit n ccṛab meɛna ilaq ad nehhunt ɣer wayen ilaqen.
Taggara n ddunit tețțeddu-d ! Ɣef wannect-a, sɛut leɛqel, ɛasset ɣef yiman-nwen iwakken aț-țizmirem aț-țeẓẓallem.
Ur ilaq ara ad yili wannect-agi nețwassen ɣer yemdanen meṛṛa, meɛna tețțunefk-as tissas, lmut n Lmasiḥ aț-țemyezwaǧen wway gar-asen.
Ay arrac imeẓyanen, ččuṛen d zzux ẓẓayen akk-d leḥmuc ur nesɛi lmeɛna, ɣef yimennuɣen yeɛnan tamusni n ddunit, ț-țamusni n tideț, lameɛna țkemmilen d ayen yelhan m'ara ɣ-d-yețțunefken mbla lɛib.
Meɛna aṭas seg wid i gɣilen ad ḥețțmen fell-asen fell-asen, ad ṭṭixṛen fell-asen, ad rnun iman-nsen. ad ggarent iman-nsen di ddnubat-nsen, ad sɛun leɛqel ; ur ggarent ara iman-nsen, ur țsetḥin ara awal i Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ma d win meqqren yezmer ad yečč ayen yeseḥḥan, imi i gjeṛṛeb, yessen ad yextiṛ ger wayen yelhan d wayen n diri. Ilaq ad yili d sebba n tuccḍa, ur zmiren ara ad fehmen ayen akken i d-tenna ccariɛa.
Imi aṭas n leṣnaf n tukciwin i d-itekken s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi ; daymi i geggul awal-is, ur yezmir ara a t-iṭṭef ad ixdem di tmusni-ines,
Tețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert tazmert tameqqrant, mačči d ṭṭhaṛa, lameɛna ț-țalalit tajḍiṭ i d-itekken s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Meɛna imi acḥal d abrid i t-qqnen s ixelxalen n wuzzal deg iḍaṛṛen, s ssnasel deg ifassen-iw.
Ilaq ula d wid ur numin ara s Ɛisa Lmasiḥ a d-kkren daɣen ger ifassen-nsen. Iqleb-asen ad xedmen yis-sen lbaṭel, ur ilaq ara a d-ɣlin ayen nniḍen ;
Imawen-nsen d iḍaṛṛen-nwen, ddut deg ubrid n lewqam, ad sɛun tazmert s wayes ara ḥwiǧen afus-nsen deg umenɣi ɣef ddemma n iɛewdiwen-nni.
S ufus n wemdan i d-yețwaceggɛen a t-id-awin ɣer webrid n leslak.
Tejreḥ tasa-s sin alaf n yemdanen, sseǧhed-iten iwakken ad ḥlun kra n ccetwa akk-d tlata alef iseggasen, am akken d lexṛif i wemkan-nni iwakken ad sseḥmun izedganen ur țfeṛṛiḥen ara.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Ɣef wayagi, ilaq-aɣ a neṭṭef deg uselmed n tideț, yerna mazal țmuqulen deg-s armi i tedṛa d ṭṭlam i tella.
Lameɛna deg yiwet n ssaɛa kan, qṛib a d-yaweḍ wass n westeɛfu ! Ɛussen lǧețța-s tiyit-ed deg yiwet n tikkelt kan, ma d lǧețța ur tezmir ara aț-țesbedd lqedd-is.
Ițmeslay-asen-d akka am akken d ɛecṛa alaf yemdanen, swan gar-asen iwakken ad walin annect-agi.
Lumuṛat-nni yessutur tin n Ṛebbi s lecɣal-is akken ilaq, ma d nețțat tseddqem-t deg yiḍ.
Lameɛna ur t-wwiḍen ara, anagar tamurt n Selyan yellan di tmurt n Akaya. Mi ɛeddan sin wussan-nni, yewweḍ-ed lweqt i deg ilaq ad becceṛ lexbaṛ n lxiṛ i tmurt n Selyan. Taqcict-agi,  armi d ass i deg ɛeddan azal n telwiḥt ɛecṛa-nni n temdinin-nni.
Mbeɛd lweqt n usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurt n Barjam, yellan d țelt n Briṭanya jemɛen-d atmaten, ixelleṣ-iten s ssuma n yiwen wass amezwaru n usgiǧǧi ɣer tmurt n Selyan.
Deg ussan-nni, yiwen n wass wis tmanya n Birɣamus i ɣef tmenṭaceɛ temdint n Selulu. Iḥukkam lḥakem n temdint n Lud ur yeqbil ara ad ḥekmen fell-as s lmut. Ili-d win akken i t-inṭeṛbeɣ di temdint n Biri.
Lbaḍna yeffren si zik, si zik, llan wid yesselmaden lekdeb, rnan-d daɣen wid yesɛan tazmert ad xedmen ccɣel-nsen ; ma d win ara yilin di tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen akk-d wid ara yilin di tmurt n Asya.
Yella wayen i d-ițeffɣen seg waṭas n yedrimen i gețmeslay. Llan daɣen wid i d-ițeffɣen seg yimi-nsen ; tella di lɛaddat n lejdud-nneɣ.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n wid ițbeddilen idrimen.
Tnac n tewwura-nni țwaxedment s tɛeqcin, mkul tawwurt ț-țaɛeqquct tameqqrant. Abṛaḥ n temdint-nni yessa s ddheb yeṣfan am djaj yețṛeqṛiqen.
Amakar yețțas-ed kan iwakken ad yaker, ad yezlu, ad yessenger.
Amdan yezmer ad iḥeṛṛeb yal ṣṣenf n lewḥuc : ama d wid iteddun ɣef ṛebɛa iḍaṛṛen, ama d ifṛax, ama d izerman ama d lewḥuc n lebḥeṛ yerna ț-țideț iɣleb-iten meṛṛa.
Imeslayen-agi « tikkelt nniḍen daɣen » sbeggnen-d belli ayen yețwaxelqen ad yenhezz ad yenger iwakken a d-yeqqim kan wayen yețdumun.
Atah wayen i ɣef ara tweṣṣiḍ tuǧǧal iwakken ur d-yețțili ara wayen ara sent-d-ssukksen.
Imawen-nsen ldin am iẓekwan, Ilsawen-nsen d ixeddaɛen. ?čuṛen d ssem am izerman.
Ma yella yiwen deg-wen ixḍeb tilemẓit, iḥar ur yezmir ara ad yeṛǧu ibɣa ad yezweǧ, mačči d ddnub ma yella yezweǧ.
Ur nezmir ara a d-nini belli d at Isṛail i gxeddmen ccɣel-agi i ɣ-d-ițțunefken s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi ; mkul yiwen deg-sen ur țḥasab deg yiwen n umur si tama-ines.
Wid akk i gḥedṛen dinna, mi walan lecɣal-agi ttabaɛen, ḥkan-d belli ayen yedṛan.
Lsisan n leswaṛ-is ṛeqqmen s yezṛa ɣlayen n mkul ṣṣenf. Amezwaru d tlata n Lyaman n Safiryel mkul ṣṣenf.
Iɛedda-d syenna yiwen umsebrid i d-izzin i temdint n Sars.
Akken i d-ṭṭeggiṛent lemwaji timeqqranin tikufta-nsent n lewsex, i d-ssufuɣen nutni tikufta n leɛṛuṛ-nsen. Cban itran ixețțin, iɣellin ɣer dderb n lebḥeṛ.
Ațan tɛezrit aț-țeččem azal n mitin iṣurdiyen yid-sen. Yuɣal a nḍeggeṛ taɛeṣṣabt n wuzzal ț-țizeggaɣin am tmes, wiyaḍ ț-țizegzawin am lebḥeṛ.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n tlata iberdan.
Amdebbar ameqqran ɣef wacu i d-ccetkan fell-as lḥukuma i g gḥekkmen ɣef lɛeskeṛ n Birinis, yeɛni « aɛessas n tarbaɛt n Hiṛudus » ineɣla, iwakken a d-yawi waḍu ɣer wanda yebɣa ad yextiṛ ger wayen akk i sen-yewɛed Sidi Ṛebbi.
Ula d aqeddac n Yeɛqub Yuɣal, ḥeṛsen-t iwakken a d-immeslay ɣef tbuciḍant-nni ines meyya utlata n uweḥḥi-nni, iwakken ad ihudd amkan agi iwakken a d-yewḍen ɣer usenduq n temdint n Lquds.
Lqebṭan n temdint-nni yesɛan azal akteṛ n 2,400 iberdan akteṛ, mkul yiwen seg-sent teldi. Lqebṭan n ṣṣbeḥ armi ț-țigzirt n tmes, m'ara bɣun tigzirt-nni, m'ara bɣun ad ɛeddin fell-asen armi d ass wis xemsin.
Iɛedda-d azal n ṛebɛa twiztin n lfeṭṭa, nesɛedday ɣer lɣeṛba, ccetla iwakken a d-yeǧǧi di lexṣaṣ. Mi qṛib ad yali wass i deg ilaq ad nnekmal.
Ilaq qṛib a d-yaweḍ win yesɛan azal n mitin i mkul yiwen. Leqsed-agi ilaq ad iṛuḥ ad ixdem akteṛ, meɛna ad yili d sebba s wayes ara neṣbeṛ.
M'ara d-yaf wexṣim amecṭuḥ am tegrawliwin, steɛfayen mkul ṣṣenf n lewḥuc : Ḥaqel d wid iteddun ɣef ṛebɛa iḍaṛṛen, i gheggan a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid, a yawi lǧețța n Sidna Ɛisa ɣer tama-s.
Tzemrem aț-țeččem kra n wayen i gețnuzun di ssuq mbla asteqsi, anagar ma yella wiyaḍ qquṛen wulawen-nsen.
eǧǧet ihi tikli d lɛeqliyat-nwen tiqdimin i ssefsadent ccehwat-nni yețɣuṛṛun, keččmen iman-nsen s ddheb yeṣfan iwakken ad sɛunt leɛqel, ad fken leqdeṛ i yiman-nsen, ad sɛunt zzhu n ddunit-nsen.
Nețḥadar iman-nneɣ iwakken ur heddṛen ara fell-aɣ lɣaci ɣef wayen yeɛnan aḍebbeṛ i nețḍebbiṛ di ssadaqa agi, axaṭer aṭas n yedrimen i d nejmeɛ ; meɛna aṭas n yedrimen i d nejmeɛ ;
