Mkul yiwen deg-sen yețțunefk as uqenduṛ d tnac wussan.
Akal yeṛwan amecṭuḥ ameqqran ! D acu i d-yețțunefken afexxaṛ seg wayen yuran di tira iqedsen : Ufan deg-s tegzirt n Kritus yekka-d yiwet n tbuciḍant, d win yessexṛaben lǧețța-s yeɛni « win yesseṛwaǧen».
